00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.370
HEIDI PITLOR: Thank you.

00:00:18.370 --> 00:00:18.720
MALE SPEAKER: Thank you.

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:20.178
HEIDI PITLOR: Thanks
