If anyone else reads more,
I think they need help.

00:01:06.170 --> 00:01:09.060
I need help, so they
definitely need help.

00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:10.630
MALE SPEAKER: She's
also found time

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:14.720
to write two novels, "The
Birthdays" and her most

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:17.830
recent novel, which you have
copies of, "The Daylight

00:01:17.830 --> 00:01:21.250
Marriage," which
I read in advance

00:01:21.250 --> 00:01:25.920
and in another month or two,
